data.description: This home is move-in ready with laminate flooring throughout the main level. Spacious living room with kitchen and dining room combo that walks to the back yard. The main level is open and bright and also features a half bath for guests. Upstairs there are 3 bedrooms and a full bath. The basement features a spacious family/ rec room with endless possibilities as well as laundry room. The front yard landscaping is easy to maintain and the backyard is  fully fenced.
